---
import { OliverParallax } from 'skiper-islands'
---

<section class="py-20 md:py-28 px-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-center">
    <OliverParallax speed={0.3}>
      <div class="aspect-[4/5] overflow-hidden">
        <img
          src="https://picsum.photos/seed/stockholm+scandinavian+interior/800/1000"
          alt="Aevo studio in Stockholm"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </OliverParallax>
    <div>
      <span class="section-label mb-4 block">Our story</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold lowercase leading-[1.05] tracking-tight mb-6">
        We've been at it since 2007. Still haven't gotten bored.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base text-brand-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-5">
        What started as a small workshop in Södermalm has grown into a team of twelve designers, engineers, and storytellers. We make watches for people who care about how things are made, not just how they look.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base text-brand-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Every material we choose, every supplier we work with, is a decision we stand behind. No shortcuts, no corners cut. Just honest design.
      </p>
      <a href="/about" class="btn-secondary">
        Read our story
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
